## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="8fc38-298">En el ejemplo siguiente se crea un <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder> objeto, anexa contenido y organiza el contenido en los párrafos y frases.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8fc38-298">The following example creates a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder> object, appends content, and organizes the content into paragraphs and sentences.</span></span>  

```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  

namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
    static void Main(string[] args)  
    {  

